1
00:00:09,360 --> 00:00:12,019
We will deliver your items at 6 p.m.,

2
00:00:12,020 --> 00:00:14,029
so please be at your new home by then.

3
00:00:14,030 --> 00:00:16,110
Yes, thank you very much.

4
00:00:16,110 --> 00:00:18,660
Goodbye.

5
00:00:25,310 --> 00:00:27,350
That was quick.

6
00:00:32,700 --> 00:00:35,839
We still have time until 6.

7
00:00:35,840 --> 00:00:40,210
Do you want to get some tea before then?

8
00:00:40,210 --> 00:00:44,869
No, I want to walk around here one last time.

9
00:00:44,869 --> 00:00:46,499
Oh, right.

10
00:00:46,500 --> 00:00:48,149
I'll come with you.

11
00:00:48,149 --> 00:00:51,220
What a relief. You're still here.

12
00:00:55,420 --> 00:00:58,600
You forgot this.

13
00:01:08,770 --> 00:01:10,430
Well, then...

14
00:01:11,380 --> 00:01:13,300
Take care.

15
00:01:32,350 --> 00:01:34,920
Shall we go?

16
00:01:37,990 --> 00:01:39,519
Sorry.

17
00:01:39,520 --> 00:01:42,010
I want to be alone.

18
00:01:43,530 --> 00:01:45,063
Okay.

19
