21
00:02:13,130 --> 00:02:16,220
♫ Gradually I become more awake like a night owl ♫

22
00:02:16,220 --> 00:02:19,190
♫ Recalling memories, I cry, and laugh ♫

23
00:02:19,190 --> 00:02:21,040
♫ But I can't tell you ♫

24
00:02:21,040 --> 00:02:23,070
♫ How all night long ♫

25
00:02:23,070 --> 00:02:25,110
♫ I'm waiting for you ♫

26
00:02:25,110 --> 00:02:28,850
♫ Fingers intertwined ♫

27
00:02:28,850 --> 00:02:32,320
♫ You keep me up now, I'm a night owl ♫

28
00:02:32,320 --> 00:02:35,250
♫ I know I won't be able to sleep today ♫

29
00:02:35,250 --> 00:02:37,080
♫ It's already past 3 A.M. ♫

30
00:02:37,080 --> 00:02:38,990
♫ The deeper the night goes ♫

31
00:02:38,990 --> 00:02:42,190
❄ Jack o' Frost ❄
♫ I can't stop being a night owl ♫

32
00:02:42,190 --> 00:02:45,940
