190
00:22:11,559 --> 00:22:15,839
Come on, Ritsu, we'll never finish like this.

191
00:22:15,840 --> 00:22:18,520
There's no rush.

192
00:22:20,340 --> 00:22:21,639
All right.

193
00:22:21,640 --> 00:22:23,580
Like I said...

194
00:22:28,380 --> 00:22:30,210
Hey.

195
00:22:31,130 --> 00:22:32,710
Yes?

196
00:22:35,800 --> 00:22:38,840
I thought we were restarting soon.

197
00:22:39,430 --> 00:22:40,863
Yes.

198
00:22:41,470 --> 00:22:46,090
For you, I'll restart as many times as it takes.

199
